Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra

Class GF2nONBElement

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra.GF2nElement
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra.GF2nONBElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
GFElement
public class GF2nONBElement extends GF2nElement
This class implements an element of the finite field GF(2n ). It is represented in an optimal normal basis representation and holds the pointer mField to its corresponding field.
See Also:
GF2nField, GF2nElement
